  "short_description": "Shooting, flying, using a shield, night vision... That is \"Shoot!\". VR shooter game, which requires a little bit of thinking. In our game, you will become a superhero, who has to save the others. Try it now and don't forget \"With great power, comes great responsibility.\"!",
